{% call getstarted.section("Overview") -%}

  <p>Our product logos connect every new product or service to our brand. Their consistent format allows us to add new product logos to our portfolio without additional design or legal costs. This library includes the following product logos. To see a repo of all logos, visit <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1mrQd094Q7kse_rDb1BpcO7RDShsauoaZjxvEf6eW1cI/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">this page</a>.</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Standard product logos</li>
    <li>Product logo variants</li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Temporary Warning alert until web component release -->
  <p style="background-color: #fdf7e7; border-top: 2px solid #f0ab00; padding: 16px 16px 16px 24px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.2px;"><span style="color:#795600"><strong>Warning</strong></span><br />Not all product logos include a variant. Use what is available, do <strong>not</strong> create your own variants.</p>

{%- endcall %}

{% call getstarted.section("Get started") -%}

  <p>Available product logos can be accessed in the Libraries panel in Adobe XD. You can search for a logo by name or by expanding any corresponding section.</p>

