{% call getstarted.section("Usage") -%}

  <h4>Product logos</h4>

  <p>Use product logos on websites or other web properties, their recommended size is at least 48px tall to maintain legibility.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='lightest') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/logo-library/logo-library-logo-examples.svg' | url }}" alt="Product logo examples" style="--example-img-max-width: 872px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Component states</h4>

  <p>Use Component States in XD to toggle between light theme (regular) and dark theme (reverse) product logos.</p>

  <!-- Temporary Warning alert until web component release -->
  <p style="background-color: #fdf7e7; border-top: 2px solid #f0ab00; padding: 16px 16px 16px 24px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.2px;"><span style="color:#795600"><strong>Warning</strong></span><br />Resizing a product logo and switching component states will revert the logo to the default size. Select a component state and then resize.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='lightest') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/logo-library/logo-library-component-states.svg' | url }}" alt="Product logo component states" style="--example-img-max-width: 677px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Sizing</h4>

  <p>When product logos with short and long names are the same height, some will appear smaller or larger than others.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='lightest') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/logo-library/logo-library-logo-sizing.svg' | url }}" alt="Product logo sizing" style="--example-img-max-width: 521px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Multiple logos</h4>

  <p>If you use product logos with short and long names in close proximity to each other, adjust the height so the <strong>hat icons</strong> are the same size.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='lightest') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/logo-library/logo-library-logo-multiple-logos.svg' | url }}" alt="Multiple product logos" style="--example-img-max-width: 791px;">
  {%- endcall %}

{%- endcall %}

{% call getstarted.section("Best practices") -%}

  <h4>Inconsistent sizing</h4>

  <p>Do not use product logos at the same height in close proximity to each other.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/logo-library/logo-library-best-practice-1.svg' | url }}" alt="Logo library best practice 1" style="--example-img-max-width: 593px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>One-color versions</h4>

  <p>Do not use the one-color version of any product logo or the Red Hat logo on any web property.</p>

  {% call getstarted.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/getstarted/logo-library/logo-library-best-practice-2.svg' | url }}" alt="Logo library best practice 2" style="--example-img-max-width: 515px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>More information</h4>

  <p>For more information about product logo best practices, visit <a href="https://www.redhat.com/en/about/brand/standards/product-logos" target="_blank">this page</a>.</p>

{%- endcall %}

