{% call getstarted.section("Frequently asked questions") -%}

  <p><strong>When are new product logos added to this library?</strong><br />New brand assets are released every month, so any new product logos will be added within one day.</p>

  <hr class="margin-top--4 margin-bottom--4">

  <p><strong>How do I request a new product logo?</strong><br />To request a new product logo, contact the <a href="mailto:brand@redhat.com">Brand team</a>.</p>

  <hr class="margin-top--4 margin-bottom--4">

  <p><strong>How do I request an existing product logo be added to this library?</strong><br />If your desired product logo is <strong>not</strong> found in this library, check if it exists in the  <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1mrQd094Q7kse_rDb1BpcO7RDShsauoaZjxvEf6eW1cI/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">product logo repo</a> first. If the product logo does exist in that repo but not in this library, contact the <a href="mailto:digital-design-system@redhat.com">Design system team</a> and it will be added within one day.</p>

  <hr class="margin-top--4 margin-bottom--4">

  <p><strong>Why is a product logo no longer available?</strong><br />It might have been deprecated depending on the status of the product. To find out more, contact the <a href="mailto:brand@redhat.com">Brand team</a> for missing product logos.</p>

